It is only in the mysterious equations of love that any logical reasion can be found.

1. it is ..., that...
  强调句
  It is my mom that loves me most in the world. 只有我的妈妈是世界上最爱我的人。
  
  It was probably him who killed Ray for Cheese.很有可能是他替奶酪杀了雷。
  
2. mysterious equations of love  神秘的爱情等式。
  
3. logical reasion 合理的理由

  Make it a habit to replace each negative thought with a logical reason. 打消每个消极的念头，找到合理的理由，将之形成习惯。

4. look down on/upon 蔑视，轻视，看不起；向下看
  
  She's on he horse,looking down on him. 她坐在马上向下看他。
  
  She looks down on people who haven't been to abroad. 她看不起没出过国的人。
  
5. 
  monumental 重要的；意义深远的；不朽的
  phenomental 了不起的；非凡的
  extraordinary 不平常的；不一般的；非凡的
  immensely 极端的；非常；极大地
  
6. I appreciate it. 十分感谢
  I would appreciate it if ..  如果..将十分感谢..
  
  I would appreciate it if you give me five minutes. 您若能留给我5分钟，我将不胜感激。
  
7. have a hand in 
  参与，帮助  give  somebody a hand 
  
  We all have had a hand in preparing this program. 我们都参与了这次节目的准备工作中。
  
8. the obvious choice  理想的选择
  I may be not the obvious choice, but we made it finally, right?
  虽然我可能不是最佳人选，但是我们最终还是成功了，不是吗？
  
  This may not be the obvious choice, but it is the only one. 
  虽然不是最好的选择，但是我们已经别无选择了。
  
9. work out 成功，有成效
  Wow! it worked out. 太棒了，车子好了。

10. I am forever in your debt. 永远记着你的恩情。
  in one's debt.欠某人的人情； in debt 欠债
  
  Why is her? She is the last person I want to be in debt.
  为什么时她？ 我最不想欠她的人情了。
  
  What? You mean we are in debt now? 
  什么？ 你的意思我们现在负债累累了？
  
11. mind is blown  好嗨哟
  My mind is blown when I'm seeing my idol. 
  当我见到我的偶像时，我开心到爆了。
  
12. live one's life just unapologeticly  毫无歉意地生活

  Life is short, each and everyone should live his life unapologeticly.
  生命是短暂的，我们都应该对得起自己的生活。

13. be longing for
  渴望，需要
  
  Our company is longing for workers like you. 
  我们公司正需要像你这样的员工。
  
14. capture one's heart 俘获某人的芳心
  make a fine catch 有眼光
  
  She's so hot and she'd totally captured my heart.
  
